caption: Have no complaints about the food or the service. I had the  chicken wings, roti and empanadas and they were all excellent and well seasoned.
the best wings I’ve ever had! We got takeout for the Super Bowl and the food was amazing. We were also given an extra free empanada and free brownie. Highly recommend

Kimpanadas is EVERYTHING. We found them at a bar in Brooklyn and they were THE PERFECT food to accompany a few drinks! I tried the pizza, pernil, and spinach...Each were amazing. Kim came to check on how they were afterward! The best!
Great food. Fresh, filling, tasty. Empanadas, quesadillas, wings, BROWNIES, all of it is fantastic.
Had an amazing meal with friends at Kimpanadas!! Kim and the rest of the staff are incredibly kind and the food is delicious. Can’t wait to come back!
The best empanadas! Run here, don’t even walk!
Everything was great! Warm and authentic.. both the food, Kim and other staff.
She’s the real deal - not just the empanadas... everything is tasty here.

These are legit!!! Some of the best empanadas I've had. They are delicious and filling without being greasy. Kim has so many interesting yummy flavors, including vegetarian and vegan options, and she is always looking to improve recipes and try new flavors.
So good. Wanna try them all.
Had the pernil empanada and the almond brownie, both were to die for :)
Great empanadas!!

Delicious, flavorful empanadas served with a smile and a lot of friendly neighborhood charm. I had a hard time choosing, but i went with the pepperoni and the beef maduro. Going for the pernil next time.
KIM IS THE BOSS. World class food. World class service. Only regret with this review is that I want to keep the spot to myself.  GET THE WINGS. Every Empanada is KILLER and Kim rotates flavors.

New to the neighborhood and stumbled upon this gem.  Truly a sports bar for everyone with cheap drinks and INCREDIBLE food.  The wings are so good you wouldn’t DARE putting anything else on them and Kim is one above the rest. Kind and friendly staff who are the best of the best.
Kim is the sweetest!! empanadas were delicious 10/10 would recommend.

Kim makes some extremely dope empanadas. I had the BBQ chicken. I love the flavor of bbq chicken and this was perfect. Came with some nice salsa and some hot sauce options.  My friend had one with meatloaf and mashed potato, an outside the box food with tasty meat and an awesome, flavorful, fluffy potato.  Kim also makes other mains like wings and wedge fries, plus desserts like brownies, which are delicious.  Situated in a great sports bar. Lots of screens, nice crowd/vibe, good beer situation.
Fantastic empanadas and such great service. I had the  bbq chicken and meatloaf. Both are awesome, but the rest of the menu looks good too. Highly recommend!
Kim was so sweet and the thanksgiving emapana is to die for!

Went to a friend’s birthday party at Finn’s Corner and Kimpanada’s was catering—absolutely amazing! I got the Thanksgiving empanada, which was delicious and totally unique, as well as the baked ziti. Best baked ziti I’ve ever had. An amazing chef and such a sweetheart, can’t wait til there are more locations to go to!
Yummy veggie and meat empanadas. Lean and lots of flavor without a lot of fat/grease.  Big fan here.

Delicious food and lovely company! Watching football game at Finn’s and enjoyed a couple different types of empanadas and the baked Mac n cheese - which was incredible! We had our dog with us and Kim was so incredibly nice to him and gave him treats and love! Thanks for taking care of us and Echo! I’ll be back next time I’m visiting!
Best Mac n cheese!!! And Kim is the loveliest. She’s a great addition to Finn’s.
Only had the potato wedges - seemed overpriced $12 for a small portion of fries. Owner was super nice and sweet - just didn't feel like I got the bang for my buck

Excellent atmosphere and service. Strolled through here on a late Saturday afternoon with plenty of seating and excellent service. The drinks were great, the food better! The original empenadas had the allure of tradition that satisfies the pickiest of pallates. If you want a quick warm bite with a group of people you love, I'd definitely stop by!
Great empanada! I got the spinach and mozzarella amd the butternut squash and they were crispy and the cheese was perfectly melted, would recommend!

A true gem tucked into Finn’s Corner! Have had the pleasure to try most of Kimpanadas Empanadas as well as weekly specials which are each surprisingly great. You can bite into each empanada and realize immediately the love that goes into the preperation of the ingredients and seasoning. They are not greasy or too flaky as they are baked. The wings are amazing and don't need any sauce. The vegetarian options are satisfying. Also took some to go and my friends loved them asking where I picked them up from. Check out Kimpanadas at Finn’s Corner while kicking back with some good spirit drinks!
These empanadas are absolutely amazing! The beef & maduro is unreal. Definitely check them out

Empanadas are good but Kimpanadas are even better! Seriously the Pernil empanada is a combination of all my favorite Latin flavors. The butternut squash and Brie empanada is also so dang good I wanna have everyday this fall.  Highly recommend!
Get the pernil empanadas! This is heaven. And Kim is the sweetest! ❤️

Kimpanadas are delicious!!! She has an assortment of different cuisines packed in an air fry pocket!!!   if you in the neighborhood and wanna have a drink watch some sports and eat some good food.. check her out!!!
Everything is baked not fried. Very satisfying and not too heavy.

We been following Kimpanadas on FB, we finally made it to her location. Worth the 45 minutes drive from Jersey. Love her wings and different choices of empanadas. Planning to return again...thanks Kim for your hospitality... Kim is very attentive to her customers.
Great service, wonderful service, comeback to see Kim she is amazing!
Awesome food. Great taste. I highly recommend, Kim is a sweet soul that makes food that'll make you go crazy. Worth every Penny!

Went on Sunday to have a drink and came across the most delicious empanadas at Finn's Corner! I love the fact that as a vegetarian she has super yummy options with also no cheese!! I had the mushroom empanada it was Amazing! Super crispy and packed with filling and flavor and might I add  with no oil !!! My boyfriend got the wings special and was going on about how great those were as well!!! Definitely a fan of Kim and her food!!
Worth the money. Friendly people. Good food. Gonna make this my regular spot.
SO GOOD.
Delicious. Worth checking out.
Wings were fantastic!! Great place
Amazing food. If you’re in the neighborhood you have to stop by and order the wings and any of the empanadas they are so good!!!
Great company, friendly bartender and amazing wings and empanadas!
yummie Empanadas....walked all the way from the BBG...and it was worth the walk...loved that they were baked not fried....Kim is a sweetheart and wish her all the BEST!
Amazing food!
The best wings in the neighborhood! Don't sleep on the Thanksgiving empanadas either. Great food and great service
Perfect food for a night of drinking! Everything is on point and Kim is super sweet!

Air fryer goods and baked wings, making this corner THE place to be for the running season. Delicious and healthy addition to the local spot with the friendliest service on top.  Finn and Kim are there for ya!
Solid Empanadas and Wings. Always a go to when hanging out at Finns Corner.
If you like food, this a place you must definitely visit!!!
Super delicious and always fresh!!!! Get yours,  don't miss out!
Amazing empanada’s
Sweetest women with delicious food in the perfect establishment. If I could give her more stars, I would !
A must have pictures look good, the taste is even better 😉
I love the  empanadas. The meat is well seasoned and flavorful. Also try the pernil and the curry beef roti.
I always new Kim was an excellent cook, but what she does with empanadas is amazing! I really enjoyed the pernil ones. My addiction!
These are some of the best empanadas I’ve ever had. I can’t wait to go back for more!!
The empanadas are simply amazing.  Definitely will go back for more.
excellent food with the love flavoring!! Love the creative and different empanada's they have
I have not tried them yet but I am sure they are delicious!
I went there last week with a friend who invited me and I was very happy with how delicious the empanadas was and the amazing mac and cheese and of course the wings. I will be back!
Apart from having great food, Kim is very hospitable and kind. Highly recommend :)
Kim’s customer service is refreshing and her empanadas were creative and delicious!
Great bar food.  Friendly service.  The wings and Cheeseburger Empanadas are the best.
The most Delicious Baked Empanadas you will ever find. Made with so much love.
Good food, fair price.
A diverse offering of empanadas that is sure to appeal to anyone. The wings are excellent as well.
So good! And cooked with no grease! 🙌🏿 #healthy #airfryerlife
Creative, delicious empanadas    The chef is very personable and will answer any questions

Kim’s empanadas were fantastic! My favorite was the pizza empanada. She also makes fantastic chicken wings that come with a veggie and blue cheese dressing! Also, They are baked and not fried!!! Yummy!! You won’t be disappointed. Can’t wait to go back to Brooklyn to have them again!!
Super delicious. Great concept. Great food.
Delicious empanadas, you can taste the home made quality in the stuffing.
Kim makes the best and most creative empanadas in Brooklyn! Charming service amazing food. It’s a must!

...the food is amazing and the choices alone will have you fighting with yourself over what to try first!! The "Thanksgiving" is amazing and the "Sloppy Joes" and "Three Cheeses" have me coming back for more. Kim is a sweetheart who takes the time to come over and asks if you're enjoying the food she cares that much for customers old and new as well as how each empanada is recieved. I will be back soon!!!!!
my first google review wings were fire call NYFD empananadas were lava call a volcanist kim was so sweet call willy wonka
Bite sized flavors of deliciousness with dippings of joy all in one serving...😋
Just simple and amazing

I'd pay double for what Kim is charging for these delicious Empanadas.  The options have grown for the beginning to a vast amount of options without losing the quality and deliciousness.  I recommend the 3 cheese which is like having a mini calzone without the guilt of eating a large calzone all by yourself.
By far thee best empanadas !!! Perfectly seasoned , generous portions , very flakey and the owner is just a gem ! Will def have them cater all my events !

Kim serves a wide variety of delicious meat and veggie Empanadas in addition to wings and other delightful surprises on her menu. Best of all, the food is made in air fryers so it is made without having to be made in oil. Definitely a much healthy way to make food. And she also does events. Check her out!!!
Kim puts so much time in these empanadas. Ask about the off-menu specials -- it'll be something new every week.
Best empanadas in the hood! Quality and good price. Kim really cares about her work and her customers and it shows.

Kimpanadas has the empanadas to fulfill everyone's taste buds! Empanadas run the gamut from vegetarian to pernil (my favorite!) to SWEETIE PIES (love the Dream: coconut and chocolate!). The scrumptious sauces add to the sensational food experience. Everything is made with fresh, wholesome, and natural ingredients that has me coming back for more!
Amazing empanadas!! I love the meatloaf Kim rocks!!
Great Empanadas, Delicious Wings & much more!

The empanadas at this spot are on point. My personal faves are the pernil (roast pork for those that don’t know), beef and cheddar and the spinach and mozzarella. Oh and if she has brownies for dessert, those are slammin too.
Had the wonderful pleasure of meeting Kim and tasting these “kimpanadas” they were wonderful!!! Great drinks perfect late night spot I love it here!!!
I tried these empanadas and they FANTASTIC.....what great flavor! Such unusual and wide variety of flavors Love love loved them
